\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

, of course, 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=1}^{M}\rho_{ij}=1$
\end_inset

.
 See appendix for detail on the construction of this equation.
 We can verify that in the limit case on one single subpopulation in the
